data.description: Explore the charm of this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in northwest Bakersfield. With a tastefully designed interior, the kitchen is a highlight featuring granite countertops, a tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a view of the spacious backyard. Enjoy the convenience of being near schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. This residence is a haven of comfort with modern amenities, seamlessly blending style and functionality. Welcome to a home that captures the essence of comfortable living in Bakersfield!
